86/沈帥青：化淡技術現突破%E3%80%80港可北上賣水？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1765586%2F%E6%B2%88%E5%B8%A5%E9%9D%92%EF%BC%9A%E5%8C%96%E6%B7%A1%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E7%8F%BE%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4%25E3%2580%2580%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%AF%E5%8C%97%E4%B8%8A%E8%B3%A3%E6%B0%B4%EF%BC%9F&d=gc4ut6WgJuY7dHPOyziR0b5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=7ad43123\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1765586/沈帥青：化淡技術現突破%E3%80%80港可北上賣水？</a></blockquote><br />\n重點係睇埋唔同𠴱截先好比較<br />\n買完有幾成冇用，但唔扣番條數就用平均價錢同海水化淡比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f047e2ad274dc0af6dc1ccfb90cacbb958261ff","tid":476395,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個海大把水，拎呢堆錢去起海水化淡廠唔知幾時先渴得死；冇左香港呢條大水魚俾錢你廣東省有撚錢發展 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成本咁高 加稅你制唔制先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n財委會過左撥款起啦<br />\n<br />\n加你稅未呀？<br />\n<br />\nON <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  衝出黎柒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日後營運成本仲未有明確list <br />\n定你眼中只有建造既成本</blockquote><br />\n貴都要起啦<br />\n賣咁多水俾我地,你想渴死啲支那狗咩?</blockquote><br />\n貴極都係受惠返香港人 水又物盡其用<br />\n唔係將筆錢益班支那狗官"},{"pid":"58ac6638625bbd8da458800f7ec7ec857a8858ad","tid":476395,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:43:37.000Z","msg":"快d cut東江水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75145bcf8fe4a780a0b69454272f9240b91d9e7d","tid":476395,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:46:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廣東省沿江沿線市民和農民少用、不用水省下來供應給港人的<br />\n<br />\n人唔吠狗都笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoj